---
layout: sports-layout.njk
title: "Local Sports Schedules & Live Scoreboards | Joe Sheldon"
permalink: /local-sports/
---

<header style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
    <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--card-accent-color); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Community Hub</div>
    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.5px; color: var(--premier-charcoal); line-height: 1.15;">Pacific Northwest Sports Central</h1>
    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.5;">
        Your neighborhood dashboard for local sports. Track live outcomes and schedules for pro and college teams, or select a local school district to find varsity sports calendars.
    </p>
</header>

<section>
    <h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--premier-charcoal); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Browse High School Districts</h2>
    
    <div class="district-grid">
        {% for dist in sportsLinks %}
            <div class="school-info-card" style="border-top: 5px solid var(--card-accent-color);">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="school-title" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">{{ dist.districtName }}</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555555; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;">
                        Access real-time athletic schedules, locations, and game times for all high schools inside the {{ dist.districtName }} footprint.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a href="/local-sports/{{ dist.slug }}/" class="school-action-btn btn-league">
                    View High Schools &rarr;
                </a>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</section>